Rule: If education is Masters or Doctorate, then income > 50k $
If gender is Male, then income > 50k $ (when other factors remain constant)
If hours_per_week is significantly increased (e.g., to 85 hours), then income > 50k $
If marital status is Married, then income > 50k $
Age variations can impact income when combined with other factors
Hours per week are not a consistent determinant for income
